  "detailed_description": "::::::::::::::::::::::<strong><u>ABOUT THE GAME</u></strong>:::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::<br><br><strong>We are currently in the Combat Alpha phase of Early Access, features listed below are planned and not yet implemented!</strong><br><br><strong>To get access to the Alpha please head to our discord and apply for a key!</strong><br><br><br><strong><u>Planned Features</u></strong><br><br>Maidenless will be an arena PVP game with Souls-like combat.<br>There will be multiple weapon types and various armor options to help you customise your preferred playstyle, whether that be unga bunga with a big club<br>or a ranged caster with a focus on aiding your allies, I plan to make build diversity a focus point!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1972250/extras/a2c93695f95120631a069a79662f2b2e.poster.avif?t=1717669675\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1972250/extras/a2c93695f95120631a069a79662f2b2e.webm?t=1717669675\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1972250/extras/a2c93695f95120631a069a79662f2b2e.mp4?t=1717669675\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Player equipment, skills and attributes will be freely changeable between matches so you can always try something new or switch your build to fit what your team needs.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1972250/extras/9f6f5ad739408d527cb471e05bd236e6.poster.avif?t=1717669675\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1972250/extras/9f6f5ad739408d527cb471e05bd236e6.webm?t=1717669675\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1972250/extras/9f6f5ad739408d527cb471e05bd236e6.mp4?t=1717669675\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
  "about_the_game": "::::::::::::::::::::::<strong><u>ABOUT THE GAME</u></strong>:::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::<br><br><strong>We are currently in the Combat Alpha phase of Early Access, features listed below are planned and not yet implemented!</strong><br><br><strong>To get access to the Alpha please head to our discord and apply for a key!</strong><br><br><br><strong><u>Planned Features</u></strong><br><br>Maidenless will be an arena PVP game with Souls-like combat.<br>There will be multiple weapon types and various armor options to help you customise your preferred playstyle, whether that be unga bunga with a big club<br>or a ranged caster with a focus on aiding your allies, I plan to make build diversity a focus point!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1972250/extras/a2c93695f95120631a069a79662f2b2e.poster.avif?t=1717669675\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1972250/extras/a2c93695f95120631a069a79662f2b2e.webm?t=1717669675\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1972250/extras/a2c93695f95120631a069a79662f2b2e.mp4?t=1717669675\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Player equipment, skills and attributes will be freely changeable between matches so you can always try something new or switch your build to fit what your team needs.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1972250/extras/9f6f5ad739408d527cb471e05bd236e6.poster.avif?t=1717669675\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1972250/extras/9f6f5ad739408d527cb471e05bd236e6.webm?t=1717669675\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https